latestIgtvVideos.caption:

I hope you all are doing good and safe.
So finally “how I shave my face” tutorial is here.
Some answers of the questions that you were asking-
-Shaving doesn’t make your hair thicker or darker.
-It gives you a baby soft skin and flawless makeup application.

Rest details you can see in my tutorial.
